{"tid":1943412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★英國女孩得知麥當勞、KFC不營業 立即淚崩心情猶如世界未日","createTime":"2020-03-25T16:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T16:54:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"063ef0be5a862ccc22d988a47574173a4fd63c3b","tid":1943412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NwPs3wd8pFun0kdqIwBhlQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzExO2g9NDAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en-US/marie_claire_729/4973704acfbbaf02f6ea357d21871388\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNwPs3wd8pFun0kdqIwBhlQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzExO2g9NDAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-US%2Fmarie_claire_729%2F4973704acfbbaf02f6ea357d21871388&h=9d01c30f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n25日起至4月7日，香港麥當勞由晚上6時開始停止堂食服務，只提供外賣和麥麥送服務，用行動來防止新冠肺炎疫情擴散。而英國麥當勞亦於22日宣佈，由23日起暫停英國及愛爾蘭境內的所有餐廳，一名英國媽媽將這消息告訴她4歲的女兒後，小女孩心情猶如世界未日般。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/McDonaldsUK/status/1241824519280566274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMcDonaldsUK%2Fstatus%2F1241824519280566274&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=7643ccc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMcDonaldsUK%2Fstatus%2F1241824519280566274&h=e93461ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/McDonaldsUK/status/1241824519280566274</a><br />\n<br />\n英國媽媽Joanna Charlton將這段有趣的母女對話上載到個人facebook上，見影片中媽媽問Layla想吃甚麼，之後便續一說出Nando&rsquo;s(烤雞店)、KFC、麥當勞、PizzaHut，中餐館都不營業了，Layla立即戲精上身，表情欲哭無淚，彷彿世界未日般，但媽媽看到Layla如此激動的反應，則在旁哈哈大笑。而最有趣的是當Layla知道連外賣服務都沒有的時候，她苦著臉說「我們真的只能吃媽媽做的飯嗎？」，然後媽媽說「不好意思，難為了你。」，究竟媽媽煮的菜是有多難吃(笑)！不知香港哪間食肆不營業，會令大家有如此激動的反應呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%90%83%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%AF%E5%97%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B4%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%BE%97%E7%9F%A5%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E-kfc%E4%B8%8D%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD-%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%B7%9A%E5%B4%A9%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E7%8C%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%AA%E6%97%A5-101117046.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.style.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2590%2583%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%2597%258E-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B4%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E-kfc%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%258C%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2597%25A5-101117046.html&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=587ad107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%90%83%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%AF%E5%97%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B4%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%BE%97%E7%9F%A5%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E-kfc%E4%B8%8D%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD-%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%B7%9A%E5%B4%A9%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E7%8C%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%AA%E6%97%A5-101117046.html</a>"},{"pid":"57f9df453160dab64d057c0e37b49ac2f65d6520","tid":1943412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072726c95f163ae906e7abd3061119044d3323fa","tid":1943412,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim